    {
      "id": "stage-03",
      "order": 3,
      "title": "Práctica guiada",
      "html": "<!doctype html>\n<html lang=\"es\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"utf-8\" />\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1\" />\n  <title>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada &mdash; Millones y valor posicional</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.css\">\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/katex.min.js\"></script>\n  <script defer src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex@0.16.11/dist/contrib/auto-render.min.js\"></script>\n  <style>\n    body { font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; padding: 1rem; }\n    h1, h2, h3 { margin: 0.2em 0; }\n    .badge { display:inline-block; font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 0.15rem 0.5rem; border-radius: 999px; background:#eef; margin-right: .4rem; }\n    .example, .task { border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 8px; padding: 0.8rem; margin: 0.8rem 0; }\n    .note { font-size: .9rem; color:#333; background:#fafafa; padding:.6rem .8rem; border-left: 3px solid #ddd; border-radius:6px; }\n    .tip { background: #f0fbff; border-left: 4px solid #6ac8ff; padding: 10px 12px; margin: 14px 0; }\n    .step { margin:.3rem 0; }\n  </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Pr&aacute;ctica guiada</h1>\n  <p><span class=\"badge\">5.&ordm; grado</span><span class=\"badge\">Ejercicios</span></p>\n\n  <h2>Parte A: Lectura de n&uacute;meros</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 1 &mdash; Escribe con palabras</h4>\n    <p>Escribe c&oacute;mo se leen estos n&uacute;meros:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $5\\,340\\,200$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $18\\,007\\,050$</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $230\\,100\\,400$</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 2 &mdash; Escribe con cifras</h4>\n    <p>Escribe el n&uacute;mero que corresponde:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) Doce millones trescientos cuarenta y cinco mil seiscientos setenta y ocho</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) Cien millones quinientos mil tres</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) Quinientos nueve millones veinte</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte B: Descomposici&oacute;n</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 3 &mdash; Descomponer</h4>\n    <p>Escribe la descomposici&oacute;n de cada n&uacute;mero:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $4\\,562\\,308 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $70\\,805\\,010 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $123\\,456\\,789 = $ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 4 &mdash; Componer</h4>\n    <p>&iquest;Qu&eacute; n&uacute;mero forman estas descomposiciones?</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $8\\,000\\,000 + 200\\,000 + 50\\,000 + 4\\,000 + 300 + 60 + 1 = $ ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $40\\,000\\,000 + 7\\,000\\,000 + 90\\,000 + 500 + 2 = $ ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte C: Series</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 5 &mdash; Completar la serie</h4>\n    <p>Descubre el patr&oacute;n y escribe los dos n&uacute;meros que faltan:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) $1\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; $2\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; $3\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; ___ &mdash; ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) $10\\,500\\,000$ &mdash; $11\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; $11\\,500\\,000$ &mdash; ___ &mdash; ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) $250\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; $200\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; $150\\,000\\,000$ &mdash; ___ &mdash; ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <h2>Parte D: Valor de una cifra</h2>\n  <div class=\"task\">\n    <h4>Ejercicio 6 &mdash; &iquest;Cu&aacute;nto vale?</h4>\n    <p>En el n&uacute;mero $68\\,325\\,174$, indica el valor de:</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">a) La cifra 6: ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">b) La cifra 3: ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">c) La cifra 5: ___</p>\n    <p class=\"step\">d) La cifra 1: ___</p>\n  </div>\n\n  <div class=\"note\">\n    <strong>Respuestas:</strong><br/>\n    1a) cinco millones trescientos cuarenta mil doscientos &middot; 1b) dieciocho millones siete mil cincuenta &middot; 1c) doscientos treinta millones cien mil cuatrocientos<br/>\n    2a) 12&thinsp;345&thinsp;678 &middot; 2b) 100&thinsp;500&thinsp;003 &middot; 2c) 509&thinsp;000&thinsp;020<br/>\n    3a) 4&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 + 500&thinsp;000 + 60&thinsp;000 + 2&thinsp;000 + 300 + 8 &middot; 3b) 70&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 + 800&thinsp;000 + 5&thinsp;000 + 10 &middot; 3c) 100&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 + 20&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 + 3&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 + 400&thinsp;000 + 50&thinsp;000 + 6&thinsp;000 + 700 + 80 + 9<br/>\n    4a) 8&thinsp;254&thinsp;361 &middot; 4b) 47&thinsp;090&thinsp;502<br/>\n    5a) 4&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 y 5&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 &middot; 5b) 12&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 y 12&thinsp;500&thinsp;000 &middot; 5c) 100&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 y 50&thinsp;000&thinsp;000<br/>\n    6a) 60&thinsp;000&thinsp;000 &middot; 6b) 300&thinsp;000 &middot; 6c) 5&thinsp;000 &middot; 6d) 100\n  </div>\n\n  <script>\n  document.addEventListener(\"DOMContentLoaded\", function() {\n    renderMathInElement(document.body, {\n      delimiters: [{left: \"$$\", right: \"$$\", display: true},{left: \"$\", right: \"$\", display: false}]\n    });\n  });\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>",
